{"tid":2199171,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如果南海可以無限填海，係東沙島填個新香港咪得囉？","createTime":"2020-09-12T03:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T11:31:07.000Z","uid":53673,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"abc073baea276cfeeccbcf5c3a7de6e277a29b08","tid":2199171,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T03:48:28.000Z","msg":"東沙島係台灣控制 <br />\n政治立場上會幫香港人<br />\n填個新香港出黎實好多人去<br />\n因為最重要係近舊香港 <br />\n好多野例如氣候都差唔多<br />\n<br />\n經濟上<br />\n位置上又可以照做轉口/金融中心<br />\n稅收/賣地又比番台灣<br />\n台灣人又唔駛驚香港人大量移民影響佢地<br />\n對台灣好多好處<br />\n<br />\n軍事上 <br />\n搞到咁大個project 到時實有美軍保護<br />\n加埋香港人加入台灣軍隊/海巡防衛東沙<br />\n應該冇乜問題<br />\n<br />\n生活上<br />\n東沙島打風機會高好多 岩晒香港人<br />\n只不過冇乜淡水資源，冇高山<br />\n冇得行山/親親大自然<br />\n不過可以去多d船P補數<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab72b2510ab141f6368f52d0dc483d5ea543d33","tid":2199171,"uid":81273,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T03:49:09.000Z","msg":"希望樓主出錢"},{"pid":"a3ac4a5bdd74124ab6e213c7317bb11bff440ba9","tid":2199171,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"1ab72b2510ab141f6368f52d0dc483d5ea543d33","tid":2199171,"uid":81273,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T03:49:09.000Z","msg":"希望樓主出錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T03:52:42.000Z","msg":"台灣先出錢<br />\n之後長遠再係賣地/稅收收番d錢"},{"pid":"72d98b3e1bb48356f8b098959b281e97b316bc94","tid":2199171,"uid":53673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"今日去東沙島街ff下先"},{"pid":"66fe1e0a0dcf957f5e449a76b7cde93d1d100af1","tid":2199171,"uid":232580,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:17:16.000Z","msg":"打風吹到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5b87cabff4b440efe6854f831dc840e29aa19f","tid":2199171,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:31:18.000Z","msg":"已經入侵東沙中"},{"pid":"ae5c9